 ATTRIBUTE="console"
       URL="ftp://metalab.unc.edu/pub/Linux/utils/terminal"
  HOMEPAGE="http://freshmeat.net/projects/ttysnoop"
 FRESHMEAT="ttysnoop"
     SHORT="ttysnoop allows one to watch other tty's or pty's"
cat << EOF
TTYSnoop allows you to snoop on login tty's 
through another tty-device or pseudo-tty.
The snoop-tty becomes a 'clone' of the
original tty, redirecting both input and output from/to it.
EOF
